# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Orbit-AI environment file
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# This file is read by the `com.google.secrets` Gradle plugin at build time and
# the keys it contains are exposed to the app via BuildConfig.
#
# Important: the app does NOT read these API keys at runtime — users enter their
# own keys in-app via the Providers / Setup Wizard screens, and the keys are
# stored encrypted on-device via androidx.security.crypto. The variables below
# are only used for AI Studio development workflows and are optional.
#
# Fork overrides (recommended for forks): instead of editing this file, set
# these in `~/.gradle/gradle.properties`:
#   orbit.openRouterReferrerUrl=https://github.com/your-fork/Orbit-AI
#   orbit.openRouterAppTitle=Your Fork Title
#   orbit.agentFallbackRepoUrl=https://github.com/your-fork/your-agent-repo.git
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Used by AI Studio's secret panel during development. Not required for the
# released APK — users provide their own Gemini key in-app.
GEMINI_API_KEY=MY_GEMINI_API_KEY
